{"cid":"1572072504832002","cha_name":"王一博","desc":"王一博，中国内地男歌手、演员、职业摩托车赛车手，1997年8月5日出生于河南洛阳。2014年9月15日，作为UNIQ组合成员出道，2016年4月加入《天天向上》。第30届中国电视金鹰奖观众喜爱的男演员。《陪你到世界之巅》饰季向空，《陈情令》饰蓝忘机，《有翡》饰谢允，《冰雨火》饰陈宇，《风起洛阳》饰百里弘毅。","schema":"aweme://aweme/challenge/detail?cid=1572072504832002","author":{"uid":"101562100101","short_id":"2014940272","nickname":"王一博吧_WYBBar","gender":1,"signature":"王一博是最酷的盖","avatar_larger":{"uri":"1080x1080/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866","url_list":["https://p29.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_1080x1080.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p1.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_1080x1080.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p3.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_1080x1080.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_thumb":{"uri":"100x100/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866","url_list":["https://p9.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_100x100.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p6.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_100x100.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p26.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_100x100.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_medium":{"uri":"720x720/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866","url_list":["https://p9.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_720x720.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p3.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_720x720.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p6.douyinpic.com/img/tos-cn-i-0813/1cd2a5be9fbf428da5c06046622ce866~c5_720x720.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"birthday":"","is_verified":true,"follow_status":0,"aweme_count":0,"following_count":0,"follower_count":0,"favoriting_count":0,"total_favorited":0,"is_block":false,"hide_search":true,"constellation":10,"location":"","hide_location":false,"weibo_verify":"","custom_verif {"cid":"1661986683079688","cha_name":"大话西游直播","desc":"至尊宝（周星驰饰）被月光宝盒带回到五百年前，遇见紫霞仙子（朱茵饰），被对方打上烙印成为了对方的人，并发觉自己已变成孙悟空。\n紫霞与青霞（朱茵饰）本是如来佛祖座前日月神灯的灯芯（白天是紫霞，晚上是青霞），二人虽然同一肉身却仇恨颇深，因此紫霞立下誓言，谁能拔出她手中的紫青宝剑，谁就是她的意中人。\n紫青宝剑被至尊宝于不经意间拔出，紫霞决定以身相许，却遭一心记挂白晶晶（莫文蔚饰）的至尊宝拒绝。后牛魔王（陆树铭饰）救下迷失在沙漠中的紫霞，并逼紫霞与他成婚，关键时刻，至尊宝现身。","schema":"aweme://aweme/challenge/detail?cid=1661986683079688","author":{"uid":"6796248446","short_id":"52","nickname":"抖音小助手","gender":1,"signature":"本宝宝暂时还没想到个性签名","avatar_larger":{"uri":"1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p26.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_thumb":{"uri":"100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p9.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p6.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_medium":{"uri":"720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p26.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p6.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"birthday":"","is_verified":true,"follow_status":0,"aweme_count":0,"following_count":0,"follower_count":0,"favoriting_count":0,"total_favorited":0,"is_block":false,"hide_search":true,"constellation":10,"location":"","hide_location":false,"weibo_verify":"","custom_verify":"","unique_id":"douyin","bind_phone":"","special_lock":0,"need_recommend":0,"is_binded_weibo":false,"weibo_name":"","weibo_schema":"","weibo_url":"","story_open":false,"story_count":0,"has_facebook_token":false,"has_twitter_tok {"cid":"1661986683079688","cha_name":"大话西游直播","desc":"至尊宝（周星驰饰）被月光宝盒带回到五百年前，遇见紫霞仙子（朱茵饰），被对方打上烙印成为了对方的人，并发觉自己已变成孙悟空。\n紫霞与青霞（朱茵饰）本是如来佛祖座前日月神灯的灯芯（白天是紫霞，晚上是青霞），二人虽然同一肉身却仇恨颇深，因此紫霞立下誓言，谁能拔出她手中的紫青宝剑，谁就是她的意中人。\n紫青宝剑被至尊宝于不经意间拔出，紫霞决定以身相许，却遭一心记挂白晶晶（莫文蔚饰）的至尊宝拒绝。后牛魔王（陆树铭饰）救下迷失在沙漠中的紫霞，并逼紫霞与他成婚，关键时刻，至尊宝现身。","schema":"aweme://aweme/challenge/detail?cid=1661986683079688","author":{"uid":"6796248446","short_id":"52","nickname":"抖音小助手","gender":1,"signature":"本宝宝暂时还没想到个性签名","avatar_larger":{"uri":"1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p9.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_thumb":{"uri":"100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p26.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p1.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_medium":{"uri":"720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p9.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"birthday":"","is_verified":true,"follow_status":0,"aweme_count":0,"following_count":0,"follower_count":0,"favoriting_count":0,"total_favorited":0,"is_block":false,"hide_search":true,"constellation":10,"location":"","hide_location":false,"weibo_verify":"","custom_verify":"","unique_id":"douyin","bind_phone":"","special_lock":0,"need_recommend":0,"is_binded_weibo":false,"weibo_name":"","weibo_schema":"","weibo_url":"","story_open":false,"story_count":0,"has_facebook_token":false,"has_twitter_toke {"cid":"1608417526030349","cha_name":"李希侃","desc":"1998年4月11日出生于浙江省温州市，中国内地流行乐男歌手、影视男演员，中国内地男子组合S.K.Y天空少年成员。\n2007年，主演少儿科幻剧《AA欢乐营》，这是他的首部影视作品。2018年，参加爱奇艺综艺节目《偶像练习生》，最终因第十三名的成绩而无缘出道；4月17日，主演的青春乒乓题材剧《追球》开机；4月27日，随MR-X发布单曲《U\u0026amp;I》，并正式出道；12月3日，发行首张个人EP《K》。2019年，获得瑞丽第6届美容大赏年度粉丝挚爱男歌手。2020年，参加少年青春逐梦同行成长综艺节目《少年之名》，最终以C位加入天空少年组合。\n2020年，参加少年青春逐梦同行成长综艺节目《少年之名》，最终以“S.K.Y天空少年”成员身份成团出道。","schema":"aweme://aweme/challenge/detail?cid=1608417526030349","author":{"uid":"6796248446","short_id":"52","nickname":"抖音小助手","gender":1,"signature":"本宝宝暂时还没想到个性签名","avatar_larger":{"uri":"1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p9.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p1.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_thumb":{"uri":"100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p1.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p9.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_medium":{"uri":"720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p26.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p6.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"birthday":"","is_verified":true,"follow_status":0,"aweme_count":0,"following_count":0,"follower_count":0,"favoriting_count":0,"total_favorited":0,"is_block":false,"hide_search":true,"constellation":10,"location":"","hide_location":false,"weibo_verify":"","custom_verify":"","unique_id":"douyin","bind_phone":"","special_lock":0,"need_recommend":0,"is_binded_weibo":false,"weibo_name":"","weibo_schema":"","weibo
